data.name: FileSystemNotation
desc: The notational conventions used to denote file system paths on different file systems or operating systems.

items.name: UNKNOWN_NOTATION
lines: No information regarding any conventions is available.

items.name: UNIX_NOTATION
lines: The conventions of Unix like file systems (e.g., /dir1/dir2/file).

items.name: DOS_NOTATION
lines: The conventions of DOS like file systems (e.g., a:\\dir1\\dir2\\file or UNC notation like \\\\host\\dir1\\dir2\\file).

items.name: MAC_NOTATION
lines: The conventions of Mac like file systems (e.g., volume:dir1:dir2:file).
